19">・试镜结束</a></p><h2 id="link1">“Activ8”/“Asobi System”新VTuber品牌</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.fcfwi9a0xl00-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.fcfwi9a0xl00-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.fcfwi9a0xl00-jpg.webp 720w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.fcfwi9a0xl00-300x169.webp 300w" width="720" height="405" /></a></p><p>招募时间：11月29日（周三）-12月22日（周五）</p><p> Activ8 Co., Ltd. 和 Asobi System Co., Ltd. 的合资企业 ANNIN Co., Ltd. 推出了新的 VTuber 项目。我们正在举办 VTuber 试镜。</p><p>属于新项目的VTuber将活跃于视频发布和分发等虚拟活动以及真实舞台上的表演。</p><p> “居住在日本的 15 岁以上女性”、“每周至少直播 4 次、每周至少发布短内容 4 次、每月活跃时间至少 120 小时”、“ “能够长期持续1年以上的人”“能够尊重其他成员并与其他成员合作的人”“能够经常更新SNS的人”“对YouTube和VTuber文化感兴趣，积极性很高。”申请要求是能采取行动、能露面的人。</p><p>单击<a href="https://audition.annin.inc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000131.000033882.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Activ8有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link2">《星光制作》第四届V歌手选拔赛</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.v7qllrlkdcus-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.v7qllrlkdcus-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.v7qllrlkdcus-jpg.webp 480w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.v7qllrlkdcus-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.v7qllrlkdcus-150x150.webp 150w" width="480" height="480" /></a></p><p>招募时间：~12月22日（周五）23:59</p><p>虚拟肝脏项目“<a href="https://twitter.com/Fire_Mountain7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星光制作</a>”正在举办第四届V歌手选拔赛。</p><p>申请者必须是18岁以上的男女，对自己的歌唱能力有信心，有歌唱经验，并且能够每周至少10个小时的直播。</p><p>单击<a href="https://virtual-land-corp.com/recruit/audition_202312/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000003.000125936.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Virtual Land Co., Ltd.新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link3">“虚拟人才学院（VTA）”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.cv2snkfarotm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>招募时间：11月17日（周五）-12月11日（周一）12:00</p><p>运营 VTuber 经纪公司“ <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”的 ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 正在举办人才培养项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/VTA_ANYCOLOR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Virtual Talent Academy (VTA)</a> ”的选拔活动。</p><p>分为“VTA常规试镜”、“VTA超级精英车手试镜”、“VTA吉祥物车手试镜”三个组别。</p><p> “VTA超级精英驾驶员试镜”适用于“具有医生、律师等高难度专业资格或同等专业知识的人员（也接受实习生和助理）”和“具有上述资格的人员”。除此之外，还可以申请条件包括：理发师、商人以及其他具有优秀技能和能力的人员（也接受学生、助理等）。</p><p>点击此处申请试镜（ <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSepJfciu6JE0BOendJa8jcXahfRc6SB7nqaJ0be6IvL2jI3gg/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">普通/无经验</a>/ <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf-PxVgSicSaqKJ2WtZ8HMJXgbES8TOjvsVGrKwOidqV1xZtw/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">普通/有直播经验</a>/ <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScOQOG3K7NYvB_ks8wzA4mskHetOWHLTin0Slkx4TAmJjbbtA/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">超级精英车手</a>/ <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe1gxT8LXmWPrzsaMoAw9dHEmrfuUgFq-cEprLL2oem-ssKKw/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">吉祥物车手</a>）。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000747.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link4">《二十三寺演》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.9o1h8ax0zylk-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>招募时间：11月17日（周五）-12月11日（周一）12:00</p><p>运营 VTuber 经纪公司“Nijisanji”的 ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd 正在为英语 VTuber 项目“NIJISANJI EN”的人才举办选拔活动。</p><p> “出道后必须能够积极工作至少12个月。”“必须有主播经验。”这是申请的必要条件。</p><p>此外，“会说日语和英语”和“会说日语和英语以外的其他语言”也被列为欢迎条件。</p><p>单击<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe9IiAUm4bTKO4_6eV5PsPRsEH9fM_icnyhkPUUjtFIuZtXaQ/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000747.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link5">《Vhigh！》第二次VTuber试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-jpg.webp 650w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-300x158.webp 300w" width="650" height="342" /></a></p><p>招募期限：未知（仅通过初选者，将在复选后告知信息）</p><p> VTuber项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/VhighOfficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vhigh!</a> ”的第二次VTuber试镜已经开始。</p><p>通过将 VTuber 的活动从中心化转变为去中心化，Vhigh! 将构建一个基础设施，让 VTuber 感受到更多的自由和个性。我们的目标是提供元宇宙中虚拟活动所需的高质量虚拟形象和社区，并从Vhigh!中创造出大量的VTuber。</p><p>接受条件包括对自己的歌唱能力有信心的人、会说英语和韩语的人、有直播等活动经验的人、每周能直播5次以上的人。据透露，100%利润将被返还。</p><p>单击<a href="https://audition.vhigh.tokyo/jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000013.000109879.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HIGHBALL PTE. LTD 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link6">《纳纳哈皮》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-1024x512.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-1024x512.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/f9fb96f4fa3fb3df50bfacb21efe2ab6-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-300x150.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/